description:
Danny takes us back to the early 2000s! First up, he talks all things The OC with Summer Roberts herself, Rachel Bilson! They discuss Rachel's new OC recap podcast (Welcome to the OC, Bitches), a reboot, her film career, and more! Next Danny talks to Trishelle Cannatella from The Real World: Las Vegas about her time on the show and returning to The Challenge All Stars on Paramount+.


Rachel Bilson Interview: 4:52ish

Trishelle Interview: 36:16ish
